DmT_ZE_Meet_Text_023_b: My name is Rauru. King Rauru of Hyrule.
DmT_ZE_Meet_Text_012_b: We didn't mean to startle you.
DmT_ZE_Meet_Text_018_b: And could we ask what your name is?
DmT_ZE_Meet_Text_022_c: You two founded Hyrule? And you're the king?
DmT_ZE_Meet_Text_015_c: It's OK. My name is Sonia.
DmT_ZE_Meet_Text_019_b: I-I am...the daughter of King Rhoam of Hyrule. Zelda.
DmT_ZE_Meet_Text_021_b:
What an unexpected answer. We are the king and
queen who founded Hyrule, after all. Or at least we
were the last time I checked.
